sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User as Web Client
    participant API as Ingestion Service
    participant Kafka as Kafka Broker Pod
    participant PinotServer as Pinot Server Pod
    participant ZooKeeper as ZooKeeper Pod
    participant PinotBroker as Pinot Broker Pod
    participant Dashboard as Grafana / Superset

    User->>API: Click / Action Event
    API->>Kafka: Produce Event to "user-clicks"
    
    Note over PinotServer, Kafka: Pinot Server consumes Kafka stream directly
    PinotServer->>Kafka: Poll for message offset
    Kafka-->>PinotServer: Event Byte Stream
    PinotServer->>PinotServer: Index & Build Real-time Segment in memory
    
    Note over PinotServer, ZooKeeper: Metadata Update
    PinotServer->>ZooKeeper: Publish Segment Metadata / State update
    
    Dashboard->>PinotBroker: POST /query (Fetch real-time metrics)
    PinotBroker->>ZooKeeper: Check segment routing tables
    ZooKeeper-->>PinotBroker: Route: Partition 0 -> Server 0, Partition 1 -> Server 1
    
    PinotBroker->>PinotServer: Query Sub-segments (In-memory + Historical)
    PinotServer-->>PinotBroker: Aggregated JSON fragment
    PinotBroker->>PinotBroker: Scatter-Gather Merge
    PinotBroker-->>Dashboard: Final Query Response (Latency < 50ms)
